description.narrative: Unicef started creating awareness and increasing the knowledge of caregivers and services providers on protective practices related to the importance of nutrition. In 2019, C4D in Nutrition supported the Deworming National Plan including also water, satination and hygiene key messages as a cross cutting area. During ‘Days with Children' social mobilization increased community awareness about the importance of an apporpiate nutrirional behavior for mothers and children. In addition, nutritional screening was supported with counseling in nutrition for the 1000 first days of life for 5,098 children under five years old. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:10/02/2020
